reviewText: This movie is usally more expencive why I haven't bought it, my one daughter loved this when she was younger, now that she has two daughters she wants them to watch it, and I can't wait to see it to lol, great price,great seller, thank you
Dint care for the movie too fakey.

What a sweet fun movie. I just hate the one song that the man and girl are singing in different keys. It was like they were individually dubbed but oh so wrong for that one....jaw clenching song near the beginning. Then it is over and the rest is so great! Definitely a kids movie. Nice and clean.. Love the costumes and the slight cultural difference. I think it was made in Norway?
Really cute movie!  If you like fantasy you'll like this one!  One warning though, it is overdubbed in English but I still think it is worth having!

My daughter loves this video, but I can't watch it.  The video must origianlly be in French, as the lips do not match the words and it's dubbed over - drives me nuts.  But the important thing is that she loves it and watches it constantly.
my whole family enjoyed this movie, as a matter of fact, we watched it twice in a row,  now that is amazing. thanks for making it avaible for my family.
